      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/major-oil-surplus-seen-this-decade-as-demand-hits-peak-iea-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际能源署表示，由于人们逐渐放弃化石燃料，导致石油需求在供应大量增长的同时陷入停滞，全球石油市场将在未来十年面临“严重”过剩局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/major-oil-surplus-seen-this-decade-as-demand-hits-peak-iea-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 08:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
